"Change Set:		8041XML-Parser-nice.5XML-Parser-nice.5:Use #keys rather than #fasterKeysNote that pattern (x keys asArray sort) could as well be written (x keys sort) now that keys returns an Array...This #asArray is here solely for cross-dialect/fork compatibility."!!XMLWriter methodsFor: 'writing xml' stamp: 'nice 10/21/2009 00:01'!startElement: elementName attributeList: attributeList	self canonical		ifFalse: [self stream cr].	self startTag: elementName.	attributeList keys asArray sort do: [:key |		self attribute: key value: (attributeList at: key)]! !